{"tid":1754523,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[選後檢討] 民主黨同民主動力","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T02:13:42.000Z","uid":44925,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"969bef12291916f3460a0cb96926c8b5a6f9af98","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"選舉完左 終於可以暢所欲言檢討下<br />\n隨便起我底睇下我係唔係5毛<br />\n<br />\n今屆民主派係區議會大勝 然而有部份選區仍然要輸 原因係在於<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撞區</span></span><br />\n而咁岩 兩個區都係有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林卓廷</span></span>支持既空降民主黨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKWy85v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKWy85v.png&h=101fa9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WmLfLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WmLfLz.png&h=773538df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帝怡選區好多人都知 林卓廷馬仔 不理攬炒堅持出選<br />\n而都善選區空降既莊榮輝都係林卓廷愛將 當區本身已經係有係都會駅業委會做左好耐既李栢棠係度 深得街坊支持 而且係絕對既民主派 而林卓廷莊榮輝仲要選舉期間不停抹黑佢為建制派<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷呢條友本身就好有問題 之前退黨風波已經睇到佢人格係有問題 <br />\n佢係劉慧卿培育既愛將 本身劉慧卿已經離地到好有問題 而佢弟子林卓廷都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇錯 你可能會問 民主黨都有權參選 咁到底點協調? 邊個判斷邊個出選?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">初選</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">謝潔泳同李柏棠都同意應該有初選 但係民主黨一意拒絕!</span><br />\n<br />\n而更加重要既係 <span style=\"color: red;\">民主動力係毫無理據下推薦左劉青同莊榮輝</span><br />\n除左林卓廷同民主黨要檢討 民主動力同樣都需要檢討!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-iad3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/76686020_10212506399773530_9162579102652170240_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ohc=HegX6rOl38wAQmhCeSNTnRtIQGWMe-25ZRwyjjQNzNqiqPugjdjxZuqWg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.xx&amp;oh=14c239a7eb8ac0e903374571ca3e6973&amp;oe=5E4432F1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-iad3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F76686020_10212506399773530_9162579102652170240_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ohc%3DHegX6rOl38wAQmhCeSNTnRtIQGWMe-25ZRwyjjQNzNqiqPugjdjxZuqWg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-iad3-1.xx%26oh%3D14c239a7eb8ac0e903374571ca3e6973%26oe%3D5E4432F1&h=d7bc1084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O08Nubn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO08Nubn.png&h=09f8358a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n網上民意固然不能作準 不過民動無故推薦兩空降侯選人又係以咩為準則?<br />\n係咪民主黨就係大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家沈醉係大勝既同時 唔好忘記 <span style=\"color: gold;\">我地本應可以贏得更多</span><br />\n同時 所有當選人記住 你地如果再自私自利唔顧全大局 我地有能力推你上去 都有能力拉返你地落黎"},{"pid":"1d075b9949660d48225680303a64bba336a7db72","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"唔可以就咁算 否則以後又再輸自己人內鬥"},{"pid":"17c9aca1dff0fbcf1ac9da7147305b8360de3d35","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:52:58.000Z","msg":"唔可以就咁算 否則以後又再輸自己人內鬥"},{"pid":"81374139d253c40ab0b598d733f65153390611ad","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"唔可以就咁算 否則以後又再輸自己人內鬥"},{"pid":"84f1df273c0a829ffd7a5264bfb2bcb411612715","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"唔可以就咁算 否則以後又再輸自己人內鬥"},{"pid":"95fbd2a975df82bc5adf354cc339f742af1af2e0","tid":1754523,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"立法會玩比例代表制仲難玩<br />\n佢地依家家唔檢討做法同研究名單真係凍過水"},{"pid":"3066a7096253ec71fced8d2d00b0550e87fe917a","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"唔可以就咁算 否則以後又再輸自己人內鬥"},{"pid":"44dcb9ad511334dd914a9184573f32a7a6864a64","tid":1754523,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fbd2a975df82bc5adf354cc339f742af1af2e0","tid":1754523,"uid":14